--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br>
 Hello and well met,<br>
<br>
I am called Glamm, Leader/Founder of The Legion of Light. We seek a few more honorable, friendly, mature people willing to fight for the Light. <br>
<br>
The Legion of Light's *Everquest Devision* is seeking new members if you would be interested in joining please post here and or look for me in game! Below is some information about the Legion.<br>
<br>
Founded in Age of Empires II the Age of Kings august of 1999 by myself. Branched into Everquest August of 2000. We have around 30-50 members with the average being around 35-40. We are a group of friends who do their best to raid, group and make fun of eachother whenever possible *friendship jabs only of course* We do our best to raid once a week and encurage participation by all members.  <br>
<br>
We seek memebers who are not only active in chat, but guild groups, events and raids when they occure as well.<br>
<br>
I feel our charter best describes the people we seek as members so here it is!<br>
<br>
We, of the Legion of Light are sworn to valor. Our hearts know only virtue. Our blades defend the helpless and our might upholds the weak. Our words speak only truth and our wrath undoes the wicked that creeps throughout the land. Norrath is our home. We are explorers, adventurers, hunting companions, questors, traders, tutors, and artisans. Our pleasure comes from championing the Light, stretching our abilities, sharing with others, laughing, and having fun. We are a diverse group and in that lies our strength.<br>
We are bound by a code of honor, good sportsmanship, strength of arms, teamwork, and loyalty. Join us.<br>
<br>
Our webpage is http://www.legionoflight.net<br>
<br>
If you have any questions and or would like to join please reply here and or look me up ingame and we can talk over any further requirments.<br>
<br>
Thank you for your time and safe travels!<br>
<br>
Forever Yours,<br>
-Glamm  <p><center>
